rows.name:
A very large wooden box was loaded
onto the Divine Beast battleship.

rows.label: tlk401006_msg0003
rows.name:
Some of my colleagues say
it's fine because it's on
the manifest, but...

rows.label: tlk401006_msg0004
rows.name:
It's an unnaturally large size.
I'm worried about what's inside.
